    "Gardner completed the text for a third edition before she died of complications of bronchopneumonia in 1946.": [],
    "The third edition of <em>Art Through the Ages</em> appeared posthumously in 1948.": [],
    "Gardner planned a book on the arts of the Americas, including pre-Columbian and American-Indian arts which was never realized.": [],
    "<em>Art Through the Ages</em> became the primary text for American art history classes for the middle third of the twentieth century.": [],
